00:04:21.410 --> 00:04:22.730
Lame de blizzard !

00:04:22.970 --> 00:04:24.840
Impact wolf !

00:04:25.410 --> 00:04:26.840
Sabot d’acier !

00:04:27.290 --> 00:04:28.080
Mandale !

00:04:28.570 --> 00:04:30.000
