00:04:32.530 --> 00:04:35.170
Radical beam !

00:04:36.770 --> 00:04:38.800
Arcane du bandit !

00:04:39.530 --> 00:04:41.840
Hall memories !

00:04:42.530 --> 00:04:43.960
